---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Work On Yourself — Spirit Media"
	description="Work On Yourself is a twelve-month Soul Care Intensive for leaders whose outer success has outpaced their inner life. Stewarded by Kevin and Shelly White."
>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-red-600 text-white py-24 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-4">A Spirit Media Initiative</p>
				<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">Work On Yourself</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-red-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">
					A Soul Care Intensive for Leaders Whose Outer Success Has Outpaced Their Inner Life
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
					<a
						href="https://workonyourself.com"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors"
					>
						Visit WorkOnYourself.com →
					</a>
					<a href="#about" class="inline-block border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors">
						Learn More
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE PROBLEM -->
		<section id="about" class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
					You built the business. You carry the influence. You've been rewarded for your capacity
					to think, decide, and deliver. But somewhere along the way, the soul went untended.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Stress became normal. Margin disappeared. Faith endured without intimacy. You are
					physically present but emotionally numb. Highly successful — yet lacking any genuine
					sense of significance.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
					When leaders like you seek help, they encounter a fragmented landscape: therapy
					disconnected from faith, coaching focused on performance, retreats without long-term
					integration. No one integrates the full journey within a single pastorally stewarded
					container.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-900 text-xl font-semibold leading-relaxed">Until now.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- WHAT IS WOY -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What Is Work On Yourself?</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
					Work On Yourself is a <strong>twelve-month Soul Care Intensive</strong> — pastorally
					stewarded, relationally grounded, and theologically centered on restoration to God as
					Father. This is not therapy, coaching, or a retreat. It is a protected season where
					leaders are <em>accompanied rather than optimized, stewarded rather than evaluated.</em>
				</p>
				<blockquote class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-600 p-6 rounded-r-xl mb-8">
					<p class="font-serif text-xl italic text-gray-900 leading-relaxed">
						"And what do you benefit if you gain the whole world but lose your own soul?"
					</p>
					<cite class="block mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-red-600 not-italic">— Mark 8:36 (FHB)</cite>
				</blockquote>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">Stewarded by Kevin and Shelly White.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- GET STARTED -->
		<section class="bg-navy-950 text-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-4">It's Time to Work On Yourself</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
					Visit the official WOY website to learn more and take the first step.
				</p>
				<a
					href="https://workonyourself.com"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors"
				>
					Visit WorkOnYourself.com →
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
